actions.message:
===================================

SERVER RULES:

• This is an English-only server.
• Do not spam.
• Do not use harsh language towards others.
• No racism or sexism, this includes racist words despite your ethnicity.
• Do not mess with pre-existing server settings if theres nothing wrong with it.
• Do not DM advertise.
• Do not beg for roles.
• Do not advertise.
• Do not cause any drama.
• Do not EXP Grind.
• Do not abuse/use @ someone. This is extremely annoying to members.
• If you cause multiple problems after being warned you will be kicked/banned from the chat and you may not be allowed to come back.
• Leaving multiple times will result in a loss of your roles and you will have to earn them back.
• Do not use your mic to constantly annoy others in the Voice channels.
• Respect everyone, especially our staff.
• Do not tag or DM staff for a useless reason regarding the server.
• No copying IntrovertsUnity's rules or channels, if we find out your server shares a common structure, then a ban will occur.
• If you mock or make a person feel uncomfortable you will be warned and if you continue, you will be kicked from the chat.
• No playing inappropriate songs in the presence of younger people.
• Do not raise your voice at other intentionally.
• No NSFW imagery or videos, unless within an nsfw channel.
• No self bots.
• Don't abuse the bot commands.
• Use bots in the appropriate channels provided.
• Do NOT tag Admins+ under any circumstances.
• Abide by discord's ToS under all circumstances.

===================================
